originalText.text: Kristen is a wonderful advisor.  Her work is very thorough and clients are extremely fortunate to have the opportunity to receive her counsel.  Being in the industry myself, it is clearly apparent that Kristen is the smartest in the room.  Her knowledge paired with her amicable interpersonal skills make her an easy option for anyone looking for a financial advisor, regardless of the level of advice one might require.

originalText.text: Kristen did an awesome job preparing us for the future.  She looked at several scenarios to give us peace of mind under different ways the world may head.  She is very thorough and detailed.  Her explanations were spot on and easy to understand.  She went the extra mile which we didn't see from others in her field.  You would be short-changed if you don't get her analysis!  Just do it!
